trans-unit.source: When used as a resource key for a data template, allows the data template to participate in the lookup process.
trans-unit.target: 当使用作为数据模板的资源键，允许以参与查找过程的数据模板。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the assembly that contains the template definition.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置包含模板定义的程序集。

trans-unit.source: The assembly in which the template is defined.
trans-unit.target: 在其中定义模板的程序集。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type for which the template is designed.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置该模板的设计为其类型。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that specifies the type of object that the template is used to display, or a string that specifies the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)] tag name for the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)] data that the template is used to display.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>，它指定的对象使用的模板来显示，或一个字符串，指定的类型[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)]标记名称[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xml-md.md)]数据，使用的模板来显示。</xref:System.Type>
